of Hollywood magic?

08:27.724 --> 08:29.857
- No.

08:29.900 --> 08:32.903
You cornfed...

08:32.947 --> 08:34.296
cornhole.

08:34.339 --> 08:35.863
[tense music]

08:35.906 --> 08:37.255
It has to be real.

08:37.299 --> 08:39.693
That's what people want now.
Reality.

08:39.736 --> 08:42.260
- But I ain't even skinned
a possum before, Mr. Shine.

08:44.611 --> 08:48.397
- You said you would
do anything to succeed.

08:48.440 --> 08:50.225
Right?

08:52.357 --> 08:54.359
- A--and then...

08:54.403 --> 08:56.579
the other part, where it says

08:56.623 --> 08:59.408
"the evil dies tonight,"

08:59.451 --> 09:01.889
guess that means
I ain't coming back.

09:01.932 --> 09:04.413
- That's the best part.

09:04.456 --> 09:06.676
Yeah, Evil Bunny--
Evil Bunny makes

09:06.720 --> 09:09.070
