13:21.365 --> 13:23.150
tonight...

13:23.193 --> 13:26.327
on camera...

13:26.370 --> 13:27.676
to the world.

13:27.719 --> 13:29.286
Okay?

13:29.330 --> 13:32.072
- Absolutely, Mr. Shine.

13:32.115 --> 13:35.336
